WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.257
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.257 --> 00:00:02.777
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:02.777 --> 00:00:06.770
Well, praise the Lord, we're going to do another prayer video with you.

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:12.400
Holy Spirit, we just thank You that You have Your way today.

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:15.268
We just invite You into this prayer time.

00:00:15.268 --> 00:00:18.600
We invite You into our prayer time, Holy Spirit.

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:20.399
We need You.

00:00:20.399 --> 00:00:22.564
Pray through us.

00:00:22.564 --> 00:00:30.948
We want to go into the deeper things—the deeper wells, the deeper rivers of the Living Water today.

00:00:30.948 --> 00:00:33.859
I don't want to just go and tread shallow.

00:00:33.859 --> 00:00:46.440
Father, I want all of You and none of me, and I thank You, Father, that today we will move things in the spirit realm the way You want it done.

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:50.836
Father, I thank You, Lord, that this is a special time.

00:00:50.836 --> 00:00:56.290
This is a time that we come before You; we come to the throne room of God.

00:00:56.290 --> 00:01:19.206
We're coming up higher with the fire, coming up with the throne room of God, taking all the care out of our prayers, throwing off that beggar's cloak, and knowing that we are seated with You in the heavenlies, far above all principalities and powers, and might, and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:01:19.206 --> 00:01:23.120
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You're the one that seated us there.

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:26.857
We didn't put ourselves there; You seated us there.

00:01:26.857 --> 00:01:31.604
We're seated with You because You said, 'Sit down.

00:01:31.604 --> 00:01:38.911
' So, Father, I thank You, Lord, that I have the opportunity to come into Your throne room today.

00:01:38.911 --> 00:01:48.840
I thank You, Father, that I have the opportunity to come up higher today, because it's only by Your blood and only by Your grace that I'm able to do so.

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:58.537
Father, it wasn't by anything that I ever did to earn it; I can't achieve it, but You say we qualify.

00:01:58.537 --> 00:02:00.389
We qualify, Father.

00:02:00.389 --> 00:02:10.053
I thank You, Father, for all that You've done and all that You're going to do in Jesus' name.

00:02:10.053 --> 00:02:25.040
Well, I was going to say, the lady that was at Billy Burke—I think it was Sunday night—it blessed me that you would send me the video that you went up there for healing and all that happened.

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:26.480
That was really cool.

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:30.120
Diana showed it to me and she said, 'Look at this, honey.

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:32.080
This lady went for healing for her foot.

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:37.333
' So we're praying for your foot, for the complete manifestation of what you've been believing for.

00:02:37.333 --> 00:02:38.822
Don't give up on it.

00:02:38.822 --> 00:02:49.085
I believe with all my heart you stand when all else there is to do is stand; stand therefore, and you keep standing, even whenever you, in the natural, still have pain.

00:02:49.085 --> 00:02:59.280
Even in the natural, when you still have whatever was going on with that—looked like a lot—but I believe that your victory is right there.

00:02:59.625 --> 00:03:05.773
You receive it by faith and you take it by faith, and I believe that's what you've got to keep doing.

00:03:05.773 --> 00:03:12.577
You've got to keep standing and believing for the victory and say, 'Hey, I'm not moved by what I see.

00:03:12.577 --> 00:03:14.737
I'm not moved by what I feel.

00:03:14.737 --> 00:03:18.859
' So I'm excited for you that you got to go and be a part of that.

00:03:18.859 --> 00:03:20.720
She said she drove three hours.

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:24.936
And then there was another man; he went, and I saw his face.

00:03:25.212 --> 00:03:33.946
He went to the meeting, and he is a person who watches the videos a lot, on my videos, and he was from Canada.

00:03:34.257 --> 00:03:39.600
So he showed us that he went, so that's cool that you all are going and being a part of those meetings.

00:03:39.920 --> 00:03:50.136
I encourage everybody who is around, if you see Billy Burke's itinerary and he is in your area, I encourage you to go and support his ministry.

00:03:50.136 --> 00:03:56.055
It really blessed me and Diana, and when we have an opportunity, we will be at where he's going to be at.

00:03:56.055 --> 00:04:19.392
I mean, seriously—not that I'm giving any glory or any praise to any man—but whenever you see somebody who is hungry and passionate about the Holy Spirit and wants to see a move of God in these last days, I always try to encourage people to go out and support that because, I'm telling you, there's not very many of them left.

00:04:19.392 --> 00:04:20.960
I see it.

00:04:20.960 --> 00:04:22.919
There's a lot of show.

00:04:22.919 --> 00:04:35.554
There's a lot of people who are in it for the money, in it for fame, in it for clout—whatever—but those that just have a genuine hunger and a heart, you can feel that freshness.

00:04:35.554 --> 00:04:36.811
You know what I'm saying?

00:04:36.811 --> 00:04:48.313
When you go into an atmosphere that is not, what I want to say, commercialized, you can feel the true, tangible, authentic presence of God.

00:04:48.313 --> 00:05:00.505
It's hard to find it nowadays, and so I encourage you: if you are in the area and he's around, I believe whenever I was there I felt a true, tangible, authentic presence of the Lord.

00:05:01.218 --> 00:05:04.764
And I can't wait to be able to visit again.

00:05:04.764 --> 00:05:18.411
I would love to go down to Florida and see him again when he goes to Tampa or to Miami, or any of those areas, especially in January and February when it's really cold here.

00:05:18.411 --> 00:05:24.109
So we just want to encourage y'all today.

00:05:24.109 --> 00:05:34.120
Diana and I are praying, we're believing, and we're standing with you for what you're needing—whatever you may have going on in your life that you think is impossible.

00:05:36.936 --> 00:05:38.463
There's nothing impossible today.

00:05:38.463 --> 00:05:45.800
So we're going to pray and we're going to believe God for your miracle, for your healings, for your time of travel.

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:48.910
You may be traveling for this holiday season; we're going to pray for you for that.

00:05:48.910 --> 00:05:50.535
We're going to pray for a lot of things.

00:05:50.731 --> 00:05:58.131
I'm going to spend less time talking and more time praying and believing with you for your miracle, for what you're believing for.

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:13.777
2025 will be a great year in Jesus' name for you all, that we stand on our covenant—that we're not moved by what we see around us, we're not moved by what we feel, we're moved by what the Word of God says.

00:06:13.777 --> 00:06:21.240
Because He said we have what we say, and we're going to say out of our mouths: 'Our year of 2025 is blessed.

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:23.690
Our year of 2025 is going to be prosperous.

00:06:23.690 --> 00:06:27.456
Our year is going to be healed and whole and well.

00:06:27.456 --> 00:06:29.059
' Whatever you may need.

00:06:29.059 --> 00:06:31.104
And that we finish strong in 2024.

00:06:31.104 --> 00:06:44.826
We've got a couple more weeks here, and we're going to live long and finish strong—time for strong living in by faith—that we have what we say, and we call those things that be not as though they were today.

00:06:44.826 --> 00:06:45.919
That's what you've got to do.

00:06:45.919 --> 00:06:50.840
You've got to call your circumstances and tell them, 'You're going to change.

00:06:50.840 --> 00:06:52.234
You're going to change.

00:06:52.234 --> 00:06:59.059
' And that moment you spoke it out—remember whenever I was before the throne of the Lord, He said, 'Say this.

00:06:59.059 --> 00:07:06.970
' When I went before the throne of the Lord, every time when I was there, He spoke out of His mouth.

00:07:06.970 --> 00:07:14.840
Every time the Father spoke something, it came out like a seed; it came out like a light.

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:24.819
Every word started to grow right in front of me; it became a seed and it started to grow like peanut roots.

00:07:25.199 --> 00:07:32.520
It all started to grow right in front of my face when I was at the throne.

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:38.879
Every letter was in English to me because that's what I speak.

00:07:38.879 --> 00:07:59.960
Every word that He spoke came out in English, and each letter became a seed, and every seed started to grow, and it became one word—all like roots that were moving, like peanut roots or potato roots or whatever.

00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:04.240
You could see the plant growing right there in front of my face.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:12.907
But every word looked like a root, and they would form and they would move out all over in front of me and they joined into one word.

00:08:12.907 --> 00:08:14.884
But they did not die.

00:08:14.884 --> 00:08:27.816
Like, you think your words come out of your mouth and they just fall flat on the ground and they're just there—well, they're just going to the atmosphere—but your words grow roots and they become powerful.

00:08:27.816 --> 00:08:32.944
The Bible says that life and death is in the power of your tongue.

00:08:32.944 --> 00:08:38.834
So how is that possible, that life and death is in the power of your tongue?

00:08:39.229 --> 00:08:43.755
That's telling you that your words do not return unto you void.

00:08:43.755 --> 00:08:49.858
He says, 'My words will not return unto Me void, and they will accomplish that which I set them to do.

00:08:49.858 --> 00:08:58.200
' So if you have power in life and death in your tongue and your words will accomplish—how would your words accomplish that?

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:17.329
Well, in the spirit realm, just like the Father, whenever I was taken to His throne, those words grow; they become life, because His words are life to those that find them and health to all their flesh.

00:09:17.329 --> 00:09:18.843
The Bible says that.

00:09:18.843 --> 00:09:29.800
So the Word of God becomes life to those that find them and health to all their flesh because your words are alive, ladies and gentlemen.

00:09:29.800 --> 00:09:32.440
Your words have power to change things.

00:09:32.440 --> 00:09:42.720
And so when you speak out of your mouth and you decree in your heart and you say those things—because the Bible says out of the abundance of the heart the mouth speaks.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:58.183
So if you want to know what's inside of you in abundance, you just open your mouth, and the more you open your mouth, what's in abundance in you comes out of you, because out of your belly shall flow rivers of Living Water.

00:09:58.183 --> 00:10:00.551
So those waters come up out of you.

00:10:00.551 --> 00:10:07.079
And what's in you—you can have some real nasty, stagnant water or you can have Living Water, but that's your choice today.

00:10:07.079 --> 00:10:10.920
You have to get in that Word and get the Word foundation.

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:13.750
The Word has to be a foundation in your heart.

00:10:13.750 --> 00:10:20.200
So the more you make that Word Living Water, that Living Water comes up out of you.

00:10:20.200 --> 00:10:22.245
Out of your belly shall flow Living Water.

00:10:22.542 --> 00:10:23.853
That's what's changing your heart.

00:10:23.853 --> 00:10:28.580
That's what gets inside your heart, is what I'm trying to say, and you can see what's in you.

00:10:28.580 --> 00:10:32.408
It's like a sponge: boop, and it all of a sudden starts coming up out of you.

00:10:32.408 --> 00:10:41.640
And you go, 'Wow, that man's full of the Word,' or 'That lady's full of the Word,' or 'Hey, he's full of bad things because he sure talks a lot of trash.

00:10:41.640 --> 00:10:52.279
' Okay, so all those roots came up out of that in front of me; they started to grow, and I'm telling you every single thing started stacking all in front of me.

00:10:59.873 --> 00:11:06.399
His words formed a line like a book, and every single time they would just stack, stack, stack.

00:11:07.999 --> 00:11:10.582
I could see it all being put out.

00:11:10.582 --> 00:11:17.540
But as they were growing, ladies and gentlemen, every word grew together.

00:11:17.540 --> 00:11:22.910
Every sentence started growing together; they became one.

00:11:22.910 --> 00:11:30.319
God didn't just speak to hear Himself talk; He speaks to make real things happen in a real world.

00:11:30.319 --> 00:11:34.040
And whenever He speaks, He changes things.

00:11:34.040 --> 00:11:39.295
Just like whenever He spoke the worlds into existence, what He said, He got.

00:11:39.295 --> 00:11:49.080
And you're created in His image; you are created in His likeness, and the same power that was in Him rests on you.

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:56.227
You have Him inside of you; He dwells on the inside of you.

00:11:56.227 --> 00:12:04.417
So as you speak, just like He spoke, that power flows through you to change things.

00:12:04.417 --> 00:12:05.669
Do you understand?

00:12:05.669 --> 00:12:25.552
So that's why I'm trying to tell you: when you decree a thing out your mouth, when you say out your mouth, 'I'm healed, I'm whole, I'm prosperous, my marriage is whole, my children are whole, my house is a happy house, I've got joy in this house, I'm full of joy, I'm no longer depressed, I have no anxiety, I have no fear.

00:12:25.552 --> 00:12:28.120
' I can speak and decree a thing out of my mouth.

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:29.577
You know why?

00:12:29.577 --> 00:12:34.355
Because the same life-giving power lives on the inside of you.

00:12:34.355 --> 00:12:42.409
Because He spoke it, just like He did in Genesis: He spoke the worlds into existence, He spoke it all.

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:44.140
And guess what?

00:12:44.140 --> 00:12:46.253
He lives on the inside of you.

00:12:46.253 --> 00:12:51.119
So as you speak to your circumstances, they change.

00:12:51.119 --> 00:12:54.847
'Well, how come I don't see it so quick, Brother Brandon?

00:12:54.847 --> 00:12:56.245
' That's grace.

00:12:56.245 --> 00:12:56.651
That's grace.

00:12:57.057 --> 00:12:58.274
You know why?

00:12:58.274 --> 00:13:00.836
Because you speak a lot of trash too.

00:13:00.836 --> 00:13:15.813
And as you bridle your tongue, as you take captive of your tongue and your thoughts and you make sure that your tongue is just not unruly, speaking things all over the place, you'll see more manifestation.

00:13:15.813 --> 00:13:22.095
What if you started going around saying, 'Well, that just thrills me to death,' and you fell over dead?

00:13:22.470 --> 00:13:23.970
What if that happened?

00:13:23.970 --> 00:13:25.650
You would go, 'Wow.

00:13:25.650 --> 00:13:37.811
' If we started seeing people fall over dead when they say, 'Well, that scared me to death,' and you got scared to death and you fell over dead right there, people would realize how powerful their words truly are.

00:13:37.811 --> 00:13:47.376
But God's grace and mercy is over that, ladies and gentlemen, so that when we say something silly like that, we don't just have the fruit immediately.

00:13:47.376 --> 00:13:57.560
But I'm telling you, if you keep saying that out of your mouth—'That just blows me away'—it seems so innocent, but your mouth is like a loaded weapon.

00:14:05.091 --> 00:14:10.035
You can speak words that are a blessing or you can speak words that are a curse.

00:14:10.035 --> 00:14:20.123
And when you speak over your children, you speak over your wife, you speak over your husband, when you speak over your finances, you're pointing that loaded weapon towards it.

00:14:20.123 --> 00:14:23.428
Life and death is in the power of your tongue.

00:14:23.428 --> 00:14:24.971
Remember that today.

00:14:24.971 --> 00:14:28.018
I just felt like the Lord wanted me to say that.

00:14:28.018 --> 00:14:30.200
He told me, He said, 'Tell about the seeds.

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:41.929
' So the seeds come out of your mouth, and when you're speaking into the atmosphere, you're creating a canvas of life or death.

00:14:41.929 --> 00:14:43.089
What do you speak?

00:14:43.089 --> 00:14:45.789
What do you decree today out of your mouth?

00:14:45.789 --> 00:14:47.702
Life and death—remember that.

00:14:48.571 --> 00:14:52.071
You have the power and authority to do it.

00:14:52.071 --> 00:14:56.150
So I say today, 'Father, I thank You.

00:14:56.150 --> 00:15:04.720
' If you say, 'Well, I've spoken a lot of bad words, I've said a lot of bad things out of my mouth, and I don't know how I'm going to get any of that back; what am I going to do?

00:15:04.720 --> 00:15:07.159
' Father, I thank You for a crop failure.

00:15:07.159 --> 00:15:19.405
I thank You for a crop failure for every single word that I've spoken out of my mouth that's been ill towards my wife, to my children, to my finances, to my house, to all this stuff.

00:15:19.405 --> 00:15:27.120
Saying bad things—Father, I thank You for Your mercy, for You said Your mercy is new every morning, and today I need new mercy.

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:34.639
And Father, I thank You, Lord, that I have what I say, and You said I'm going to call a crop failure over those words.

00:15:34.639 --> 00:15:47.085
Father, I pray mercy over those words that I have spoken out of my mouth, and I receive it by faith that I have a crop failure over my bad words that I have spoken against anybody.

00:15:47.085 --> 00:15:48.491
Thank You, Lord.

00:15:48.491 --> 00:15:59.085
I now bless them in the name of Jesus, and I send blessing over those words, because as I speak, it's turning the thing around, and those other words, they're just falling to the ground.

00:15:59.085 --> 00:16:00.1000
And then you take communion over it.

00:16:00.1000 --> 00:16:06.053
You take communion over it and say, 'Father, I take mercy over this,' and you plead the blood over it, and you move on.

00:16:06.053 --> 00:16:09.413
You don't worry about it; you don't take care over it.

00:16:09.413 --> 00:16:12.423
You just change the direction of your mouth.

00:16:12.423 --> 00:16:14.795
You change the direction of your mouth.

00:16:14.795 --> 00:16:28.650
That's why I always say Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief, but was strong in faith, giving glory to God, being fully persuaded that what God has promised, He is able also to perform it in your life.

00:16:28.650 --> 00:16:40.320
So I believe with all my heart today: you have the power of life and death in your tongue, and faith calls those things that be not as though they were, and you're calling it to be not as though they were.

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:46.404
I speak it out of my mouth: I am free from whatever I need to be free from.

00:16:46.404 --> 00:16:50.000
So say that out of your mouth today, and I hope that blessed you.

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:57.669
So those seeds became like a canvas and they all started growing and they went into the Living Water.

00:17:01.097 --> 00:17:03.084
People go, 'What happened to the words?

00:17:03.084 --> 00:17:11.328
' They started growing roots and they tapped into—there was a big pool of water, a big pool of Living Water all at the throne of the Father.

00:17:11.328 --> 00:17:18.177
And it was ankle-deep, knee-deep, waist-deep, and then it went all the way down.

00:17:18.177 --> 00:17:29.540
And you could go all the way down to the bottom of that pool and you could see that pool all the way; it was the most beautiful, crystal-clear water I've ever seen before.

00:17:29.540 --> 00:17:35.200
And it's like what I've said before: you just wanted to get a big cup of it and just drink, drink, drink.

00:17:36.663 --> 00:17:39.260
And that water is there for you today.

00:17:39.260 --> 00:17:43.276
That water is there for you—that clear water where you could see all the way to the bottom.

00:17:43.276 --> 00:17:49.460
And the Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, you've been all the way to the bottom of that before.

00:17:49.460 --> 00:17:53.040
You've been in the deep waters before, and it's time for you to go back.

00:17:53.040 --> 00:18:00.240
It's time for you to get out of the knee-deep, ankle-deep, waist-deep, and go clear to the bottom.

00:18:00.240 --> 00:18:08.783
' In these last days, ladies and gentlemen, it's going to take us being filled with the Holy Spirit and staying in that deeper water with Him.

00:18:08.783 --> 00:18:21.840
And those roots that I saw, those peanut roots—all those roots that were growing, all those words that were growing before me started growing in words, and they were all looking for the Living Water.

00:18:21.840 --> 00:18:27.280
The word even out of His mouth was looking for the water of Him.

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:36.070
They were looking because the more He spoke it, the more they started to grow, and they went and they were finding the source of how to stay alive.

00:18:36.070 --> 00:18:46.480
And even His words knew—the Father's words knew—that they had to stay in the water, the water of who He is.

00:18:46.480 --> 00:18:47.874
He is the Living Water.

00:18:47.874 --> 00:18:49.611
They abided in Him.

00:18:49.611 --> 00:18:57.785
His words remained in Him, and they went and they started growing and they got in that water and they became life.

00:18:57.785 --> 00:19:03.040
His words are life to those that find them and health to all their flesh.

00:19:03.040 --> 00:19:05.646
And I'm telling you, His words are powerful.

00:19:06.377 --> 00:19:07.840
What is He speaking?

00:19:07.840 --> 00:19:10.760
What are His thoughts towards you today, ladies and gentlemen?

00:19:10.760 --> 00:19:20.354
His thoughts are—just like Diana said in the video yesterday—His thoughts are more than the grains of sand upon this earth towards you.

00:19:20.354 --> 00:19:21.177
Good thoughts.

00:19:21.177 --> 00:19:23.514
He doesn't think bad thoughts towards you.

00:19:23.514 --> 00:19:30.387
He has amazing thoughts for you: thoughts of prosperity, thoughts of success, thoughts of wholeness.

00:19:30.387 --> 00:19:33.556
'Man, I have a plan for them in a thousand years.

00:19:33.818 --> 00:19:37.420
I have a plan for them after the thousand years.

00:19:37.420 --> 00:19:41.372
I have so much for them for the eons and eons of time.

00:19:41.372 --> 00:19:45.850
' He has that for that woman right there and him right there and that one right there.

00:19:45.850 --> 00:19:48.240
And He thinks all these thoughts towards you.

00:19:48.240 --> 00:19:51.966
The Bible says all the time His mind is massive.

00:19:51.966 --> 00:19:59.640
Of course, you know He's infinite in His capacity and His ability to think.

00:19:59.640 --> 00:20:07.710
We're created and made in His image, ladies and gentlemen, so we think a lot of thoughts every single day, but just think about it: our Father thinks a lot about you.

00:20:07.710 --> 00:20:12.211
And there's billions of us; He thinks about us because He's an infinite God.

00:20:12.211 --> 00:20:15.940
Nothing's too big for Him and nothing's too small.

00:20:15.940 --> 00:20:20.080
Remember that: all things are possible to him that believes.

00:20:20.080 --> 00:20:25.550
When you're believing for your miracle today, don't believe for tomorrow; believe for the now.

00:20:25.550 --> 00:20:27.600
And begging is not believing.

00:20:27.600 --> 00:20:30.320
We're not begging God to do something today for us.

00:20:30.320 --> 00:20:33.264
You're not out there, 'Oh, God, I need it, please!

00:20:33.264 --> 00:20:34.743
Oh, God, help me!

00:20:34.743 --> 00:20:35.039
' No.

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:38.817
'God, I thank You that You said in Your Word...

00:20:38.817 --> 00:20:41.703
' Remember: always mirror His Word.

